Title: The Quest for the Enchanted Amulet

Characters: Lily, Finn, The Dragon King

Act 1

The village of Dragonstone is being harrased by a dragon. 
Lily and Finn enter a cave to find the Enchanted Amulet.
The Dragon King appears to guard the amulet.
Lily weakens the dragon with her magic while Finn steals the amulet.
The duo escapes the cave with the dragon in pursuit.

Act 2

The dragon chases Lily and Finn outside the cave.
Lily uses the amulet to create a shield and shrinks the dragon.
The duo watches as the dragon flies away, now harmless.
LLily and Finn realize the error of their ways and go to apologize to the Dragon King.
The Dragon King, hurt and betrayed, initially rejects their apology.
Lily and Finn prove their sincerity by offering the amulet back to the dragon and promising to never harm him again.
The Dragon King forgives them, and together they use the amulet to protect the kingdom from outside threats.
The trio becomes inseparable, and the Dragon King finally finds the companionship he's been seeking all along.
